sql:
SELECT dimension_id, MAX(usage_date) AS most_recent_usage_date
FROM time_dimension_usage
GROUP BY dimension_id;

external_knowledge:
- Time dimensions are categorized based on their roles in conversion rules, formula definitions, and usage events;
- The query identifies the top-ranked time dimensions in each of these categories;
- A time dimension can be significant in multiple categories.

